# Public function documentation

Add XML documentation comments (`/// <summary>...</summary>`) to every `public` member:

- `public` methods
- `public` constructors
- `public` properties/indexers/events (if you expose them publicly)

The minimum expected shape is:

```csharp
/// <summary>One-sentence description.</summary>
/// <param name="x">Meaning of the parameter.</param>
/// <returns>What the method returns.</returns>
public int MyMethod(...)
```

If a parameter/return is not relevant, omit the corresponding tag, but keep a `summary`.

